    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Shopping List \u2014 Mealie \u2192 Home Assistant\n\nListens for Mealie Apprise event notifications (via json:// URL).\nMealie sends document_data with item IDs \u2014 the workflow fetches\nfull item details from the Mealie API, then syncs to HA.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Receive Apprise JSON webhook from Mealie\n2. Parse document_data to extract operation + item ID\n3. Fetch item details from Mealie API (for create/update)\n4. Cache item names in static data (for delete lookups)\n5. Push change to HA Shopping List\n\n**Loop prevention:**\n- Items with extras.synced_from = n8n are skipped\n- Deletes use cached names; missed deletes handled by reconciliation",
        "width": 520,
        "height": 380
      },
